# Monorepo Commands Cheat‑Sheet

Refer to [CLAUDE.md](mdc:CLAUDE.md) and [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md).

## Root
- `npm run dev` – start backend + frontend
- `npm run build` – build all
- `npm run test` – run all tests
- `npm run lint` – lint all
- `npm install:all` – install deps
- Docker: `npm run docker:up | down | logs`
- Prisma: `npm run prisma:migrate | studio | generate`
- E2E: `npm run test:e2e`, `:headed`, `:smoke`

## Backend (`/backend`)
- `npm run dev` | `dev:simple`
- `npm run test` | `test:watch` | `test:coverage`
- `npm run lint`
- DB: `npm run db:init | db:test | prisma:studio | prisma:reset`

## Frontend (`/frontend`)
- `npm run dev | build | preview`
- Tests: `npm run test | test:watch | test:ui | test:coverage`
- Lint: `npm run lint`

## Testing Discipline
- TDD order: write failing tests, then implement.
- Coverage target: >80% critical paths.
